---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-[#e3d8c6] bg-[#f3ede1] py-16">
	<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1120px] px-4">
		<div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
			<div>
				<h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-[#2d251f]">Bizness Kundalik</h3>
				<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6f6458]">
					O'zbekistondagi tadbirkorlar uchun bilim va tajriba almashish platformasi.
					Biznes dunyosidagi eng so'nggi yangiliklar va foydali maslahatlar.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h4 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#2d251f]">Navigatsiya</h4>
				<ul class="space-y-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6f6458]">
					<li><a href="/" class="transition-colors hover:text-[#2d251f]">Bosh sahifa</a></li>
					<li><a href="/#categories" class="transition-colors hover:text-[#2d251f]">Kategoriyalar</a></li>
					<li><a href="/#about" class="transition-colors hover:text-[#2d251f]">Biz haqimizda</a></li>
					<li><a href="/#contact" class="transition-colors hover:text-[#2d251f]">Biz bilan bog'lanish</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h4 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#2d251f]">Bog'lanish</h4>
				<ul class="space-y-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6f6458]">
					<li>info@biznesskundalik.uz</li>
					<li>Telegram: @biznesskundalik</li>
					<li>Toshkent, O'zbekiston</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mt-10 border-t border-[#e3d8c6] pt-6 text-center text-sm text-[#6f6458]">
			<p>&copy; {currentYear} Bizness Kundalik. Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
